name: Relationship Issues
desciption: The transcendence of psychological factors of the doctor-patient relationship is given by the fact of its influence on results and quality of medical care, improvement in compliance, satisfaction and recall of physician information.

name: Anxiety Issues
desciption: Psychotherapy. Also known as talk therapy or psychological counseling, psychotherapy involves working with a therapist to reduce your anxiety symptoms. It can be an effective treatment for anxiety.

name: Psychologist Issues
desciption: Psychologists, who study how people work on their problems, break down problem solving into a series of stages or mental processes. While there are many types of mental distress and their gravity also differs, it is considered that people more or less follow a similar pattern in solving problems.
